{"tid":905712,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個食煙唔應該做嘅職業","createTime":"2018-11-17T10:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T03:16:16.000Z","uid":191765,"like":51,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"77449bbf71391622b73237aa2d985b405d2d4ddb","tid":905712,"uid":191765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:59:46.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n髮型師<br />\n屌你今日去剪頭髮，已經唔係去街市、地鐵站嗰啲地方剪。<br />\n去到間髮廊剪個頭髮都要兩舊水，一開始剪都冇乜問題，未聞到啲咩味。之後吹頭嗰陣就嚟料，佢一吹，佢手指啲煙味即刻飛哂出嚟，臭撚到。<br />\n唔敢想像啱啱佢一直用隻咁撚臭咁多焦油嘅手係噤掂我啲頭髮。<br />\n食煙就咪撚做髮型師咁撚缺徳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算你真係食 大佬你食撚完洗手吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a2712d9adac19ec4d15badfe917805f0fac1d8","tid":905712,"uid":36106,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:02:47.000Z","msg":"教師"},{"pid":"31bb98623aeb8d752f14a72891950bd8cc27457a","tid":905712,"uid":218415,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:05:39.000Z","msg":"廚房<br />\n初中食味千拉麵<br />\n湯通粉有煙灰頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1862197d68bf6e9322e2312015349dfd44dee108","tid":905712,"uid":198165,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:06:06.000Z","msg":"你想像下佢打完飛機成手都係再幫你剪頭髮<br />\n係咪覺得煙味冇乜嘢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1551c22e5562a6c66f5677bd0e3e6d2f9abd3073","tid":905712,"uid":219809,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T11:08:51.000Z","msg":"賣煙"},{"pid":"626f01ed6eb406e8246e6986709eca87f6d0d1fe","tid":905712,"uid":185583,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"77449bbf71391622b73237aa2d985b405d2d4ddb","tid":905712,"uid":191765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T10:59:46.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n髮型師<br />\n屌你今日去